=== 剧集名 ===
《新闻编辑室》的试播集还在拍摄的时候，曾一度被命名为《越往后越多》。<ref>{{cite web |title=This Just In: Aaron Sorkin's HBO Newsroom Drama Has a New Title |url=http://www.hollywood.com/news/This_Just_In_Aaron_Sorkins_HBO_Newsroom_Drama_Has_a_New_Title/11671197 |publisher=Hollywood.com |first=Michael |last=Arbeiter |date=2011-12-22 |accessdate=2011-12-22 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130103134641/http://www.hollywood.com/news/This_Just_In_Aaron_Sorkins_HBO_Newsroom_Drama_Has_a_New_Title/11671197 |archivedate=2013-01-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref> 之后在2011年11月29日，HBO向[[美国专利及商标局|美国专利及商标局]]注册了“新闻编辑室”的商标。<ref name="tvn2">{{cite web |title=Will HBO and Aaron Sorkin Draw Canada's Ire With The Name Of Their New Show 'Newsroom'? |url=http://www.mediabistro.com/tvnewser/will-hbo-and-aaron-sorkin-draw-canadas-ire-with-the-name-of-their-new-show-newsroom_b101243 |publisher=TV Newser |first=Alex |last=Weprin |date=2011-12-06 |accessdate=2011-12-22 |archive-date=2012-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120108165849/http://www.mediabistro.com/tvnewser/will-hbo-and-aaron-sorkin-draw-canadas-ire-with-the-name-of-their-new-show-newsroom_b101243 |dead-url=no }}</ref>这个新名字很快被用来和肯·克里曼创作的加拿大同名电视喜剧相比较，后者在[[CBC|CBC]]和[[PBS|PBS]]上播放。<ref name="tvn2" /><ref>{{cite web |title=Anyone remember 'The Newsroom'? |url=http://jimromenesko.com/2011/12/06/the-newsroom/ |publisher=JimRomenesko.com |date=2011-12-06 |first=Jim |last=Romenesko |authorlink=Jim Romenesko |accessdate=2011-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120503015202/http://jimromenesko.com/2011/12/06/the-newsroom/ |archive-date=2012-05-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>《新闻编辑室》的命名最终在2011年12月21日HBO的一个宣传2012年新剧的活动上确定。<ref name="seriesname">{{cite web |title=Aaron Sorkin's New HBO Series Gets Title: 'The Newsroom' |url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/12/aaron-sokins-new-hbo-series-gets-title-the-newsroom/ |publisher=Deadline.com |date=2011-12-21 |first=Nellie |last=Andreeva |accessdate=2011-12-22 |archive-date=2012-02-25 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65hviDQcx?url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/12/aaron-sokins-new-hbo-series-gets-title-the-newsroom/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

海梅·温曼在《[[Maclean's|Maclean's]]》杂志上撰文称这个命名“有一点冷酷而有趣的提醒了人们，美国的电视产业还没完全取代加拿大...加拿大的那个《新闻编辑室》被认为是加拿大史上最伟大的电视节目，但是一个美国电视台并不惧怕如此直接的比较：就算有人已经听说过那个节目，他们可能以为这个国家大多数人没有听过。”<ref>{{cite web |title=Americans don't take us serious |url=http://www2.macleans.ca/2011/12/22/americans-dont-take-us-serious/ |work=Maclean's |date=2011-12-22 |first=Jaime |last=Weinman |accessdate=2011-12-26 |archive-date=2011-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111223025314/http://www2.macleans.ca/2011/12/22/americans-dont-take-us-serious/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

